WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.602
The world of work is undergoing a profound transformation driven

00:00:04.602 --> 00:00:09.204
by Artificial Intelligence. We are moving into the era of

00:00:09.204 --> 00:00:13.806
Agentic AI, where AI systems act autonomously within multistep workflows.

00:00:13.806 --> 00:00:18.408
Consider a brief A vs B comparison. Option A: A

00:00:18.408 --> 00:00:23.010
leader spends hours manually assigning tasks to employees. Option B:

00:00:23.010 --> 00:00:27.612
A leader orchestrates a workflow where Agentic AI handles routine

00:00:27.612 --> 00:00:32.214
tasks, allowing employees to focus on complex problem-solving. Option B

00:00:32.214 --> 00:00:36.816
represents the future of human-AI symbiosis.
